measurements.description: Nine stately flowers on two up to 27-cm arching inflorescences; sepals and petals soft pink-lavender, faded to white basally, sepals linear, recurved basally, petals ruffled marginally, prominent midrib; lip ruffled, sidelobes closed over column, magenta, light pink picotee, two eyes spots rich yellow fading to white, throat light yellow, magenta veins; column pale pink, anther cap white, pink spot centrally; substance medium; texture crystalline.
